data.description: LOOKING FOR THE FEEL OF A SMALL TOWN, BUT CONVENIENT TO THE BIG CITY ? YOU HAVE FOUND IT. THIS 3 BED 2 BATH DREAM MAKER IS LOCATED IN FLORESVILLE ,TEXAS. 25 MINUTES FROM SAN ANTONIO,AND ONLY  FIVE MINUTES FROM THE LOCAL  HEB AND WAL MART. SITUATED NEAR THE CENTER OF DOWNTOWN FLORESVILLE, THIS 1250 SF. CHARMER IS PERFECT FOR FIRST TIME HOMEBUYERS, SMALL FAMILIES, OR FOLKS LOOKING TO SIMPLIFY AND DOWNSIZE. WALKING DISTANCE TO DOWNTOWN RESTAURANTS AND SHOPS, AS WELL AS TWO LOCAL CHURCHES, THE LOOK AND FEEL OF SMALL TOWN USA AWAITS YOU AND YOURS. ENJOY THE LACK OF THE HUSTLE AND BUSTLE WHILE YOU SIT UNDER THE OVERSIZED BACK PATIO IN THE SPACIOUS BACK YARD.  YOUR DREAM IS NOW A REALITY, WELCOME HOME.
